data.description: Check out this stunning recently renovated modern farmhouse just second row from the deepwater access of Boyd's Creek. This exquisite 4-bedroom 3 bath chic home offers a picturesque view on almost an acre of outdoor space with no HOA. Quality craftsmanship is evident throughout the home, with shaker cabinets, granite countertops, shiplap walls, LVP flooring, crown molding, and wrought iron balusters as well as a Water Softener System and Upgraded Septic System. Modern amenities, breathtaking views, and a boater's dream location make it the perfect blend of elegance and country living.
